HUNGARY JAN - AUG 96 TRADE GAP $ 2 BLN - TRADE MIN . Hungary ' s trade deficit was $ 2 billion in the January - August period , down $ 200 million from the same period of 1995 , the Ministry of Industry and Trade said in a statement on Thursday . The figure was a rough estimate and the ministry said it would provide a more precise figure later in the day . - - Budapest newsroom + + 36 1 327 4040 
